org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.units.requests

Class SWFTagsRequestResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.units.requests.SWFTagsRequestResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRequestResult, ISWFTagsRequestResult

    public class SWFTagsRequestResult
extends Object
implements ISWFTagsRequestResult
    Create a DoABC SWF tag for the given ABC byte code. The addToFrame(SWFFrame) call back method will add the DoABC tag to a frame.
